main event: A UFO resembling a flood light with erratic motion was observed over Momence, Illinois for over 15 minutes.
interesting points: The object was observed in the East at about 25 degrees elevation for 4.5 minutes.,The object changed color from white to red occasionally.,It appeared to expand and contract during the observation.,It was seen by about 15 other witnesses in the area.,The conclusion suggested the object was an astronomical phenomenon, specifically Venus.
witness description: Witness described the object as changing colors and having erratic motion.
